[{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Interactive exercises are enclosed in an "}, {"t": "Code", "c": [["", [], []], "exercise"]}, {"t": "Str", "c": " box. Within the box one or more question elements are placed."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Also an ID needs to be added per exercise. The ID has to be unique within the document. It can be used to reference questions from other parts of the course."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "::: {.exercise #EX_DUMMY}\n[CONTENT]\n:::"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Result"}]}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["EX_DUMMY", ["exercise"], [["data-number", "2.7.1"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "[CONTENT]"}]}]]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "The box typically includes the exercise text and one or more questions. Optionally, hints, the solution, a button for checking the answer and other content can be presented."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "The total achievable score of an exercise is the sum of the points of all the containing questions."}]}, {"t": "Div", "c": [["example-2.7.2", ["example"], [["data-number", "2.7.2"]]], [{"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Below is a complete example of an exercise."}]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{"t": "Str", "c": "Markdown"}]}]}, {"t": "CodeBlock", "c": [["", ["markdown"], []], "::: {.exercise #EX_FULL}\nWhich term is formed if the following object is inserted into the term\n$x^2+y^2$?\n\nThe angle $\\alpha$ both for $x$ and $y$: Then\n$x^2+y^2$$\\;\\;=\\;$[]{.question .text length=\"13\" solution=\"2*alpha^2\" supporting-points=\"5\" variables=\"alpha\" precision=\"5\" validation=\"mathExpression\" points=\"4\"}.\n\n:::: {.hint-text}\nThe Greek letter $\\alpha$ can be entered as `alpha`.\n::::\n\n:::: {.hint}\n$x^2+y^2=\\alpha^2+\\alpha^2=2\\alpha^2$\n::::\n:::"]}, {"t": "Para", "c": [{"t": "Strong", "c": [{